# OpenMC runtime artifacts (large/regenerable)
statepoint.*.h5
summary.h5
tallies.out
*.xml.gz

# Agent run instance outputs are regenerable. Only the curated evaluation/
# and inspect/ fixture directories stay tracked; ignore every other run
# directory under data/runs/ (VERA1, case3, manual, future instances).
# Patterns above (statepoint/summary/tallies) are extension-based and
# already match at any depth.
data/runs/*/
!data/runs/evaluation/
!data/runs/inspect/

# Plan-generation artifacts (regenerable) at root or any nested run dir,
# kept explicit in case a run lands outside data/runs/ or a plan file is
# written at the data/runs/ root rather than inside an instance dir.
**/plan_artifacts/
**/simulation_plan.json

# Local planning notes — keep private, do not track
Plan.md
